      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense for the debate prep. to make the argument really \"bulletproof\" for the competition, could you expand on that bit about \"maintaining property values\"? like, how would a debater argue that these policies actually helped stabilize the broader economy or protected the investments of the middle class? focus on the logical/economic justifications that were used to defend it at the time.",
